      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulated hemolysis index within 15% of experimental mean across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) values compared against published experimental data at all 5 flow-speed combinations. Maximum deviation 9.3%; mean deviation 5.1%. Exceeds acceptance criterion."
